org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.dictionary

Class JdbcRareWordDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.dictionary.AbstractRareWordDictionary
      • org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.dictionary.JdbcRareWordDictionary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RareWordDictionary

    public final class JdbcRareWordDictionary
extends AbstractRareWordDictionary
    Preferred dictionary to use for large collections of terms. Column indices within the database are constant and not configurable: CUI TUI RINDEX TCOUNT TEXT RWORD If a configurable implementation is desired then create an extension. Author: SPF Affiliation: CHIP-NLP Date: 3/26/13
